}],"title":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of tag","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"tag","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TagComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"tags","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") ,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") , sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizesSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}}}